comments: Brooks (MEM) legally contests Doncic's (DAL) jump shot attempt.
Doncic (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position as he defends Morant's (MEM) driving shot attempt.  Doncic then steals the ball from Morant as he returns to the floor.
As Brunson (DAL) lowers his upper body and dribbles into Brooks (MEM), Brooks makes marginal contact with Brunson as he ends his dribble.
Brooks (MEM) is established in Porzingis' (DAL) path as Porzingis is able to slip most of the contact and complete his driving shot attempt.
Kleber (DAL) makes marginal contact with Valanciunas' (MEM) body during his shot attempt.
Valanciunas (MEM) and Porzingis (DAL) simultaneously makes contact with the ball and as Porzingis tries to secure the rebound away from Valanciunas marginal contact occurs.
Porzingis (DAL) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Brooks' (MEM) path.
Valanciunas (MEM) legally contest Doncic's (DAL) driving shot attempt.
Doncic (DAL) commits a take foul on Morant (MEM).
Kleber (DAL) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Brooks' (MEM) path.
Valanciunas (MEM) commits a take foul on Doncic (DAL).
Valanciunas (MEM) makes contact with Doncic's (DAL) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Porzingis (DAL) makes contact with the ball as Valanciunas (MEM) tries to secure the rebound.
Finney-Smith (DAL) commits a take foul on Allen (MEM).
Brooks (MEM) engages then disengages with Powell (DAL) during the reobund.
As Brooks (MEM) moves alongside Doncic (DAL), he makes marginal leg to leg contact with Doncic on the dribble prior to the gather.
